::Autofire::

Autofire flies to the side, the shot from DrillBit missing him. He growls, 
flying backwards as KitKat opens fire on him, a few shots hitting him in the 
leg. His eyes narrow, Autofire continuing to fly backwards from Terrorsaur. 
Those Preds thought they could defeat HIM?

His puts away his sword, grabbing two chain guns. He fires with both chain 
guns, one at DrillBit and the other at KitKat, also firing his shoulder 
cannon and optic lasers at Terrorsaur.
